      "value": "<p>You unnerve your spell’s victim with odd gestures, cackling laughter, or other effects.</p>\n<p><strong>Prerequisites</strong>: Cha 15, Intimidate 5 ranks, ability to cast spells.</p>\n<hr />\n<p><strong>Benefit</strong>: As a reaction when a creature fails a saving throw against a spell you cast this round, you can attempt an Intimidate check to demoralize that creature. You can target only one creature regardless of how many creatures your spell affected, and a given creature can’t be targeted by this ability more than once per day.</p>"
